sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" const Table = (props) => { return ( < table className='table table-striped table-dark' > {console.log(props.keys)} {props.keys.forEach(key => ({key}) )} {/* customerID companyName contactName contactTitle address city region postalCode phone country fax */} {props.data.map((item, i) => ( {item.customerID} {item.companyName} {item.contactName} {item.contactTitle} {item.address} {item.city} {item.region} {item.postalCode} {item.phone} {item.country} {item.fax} ))} ) } export default Table;
